OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry evening
OL,6,Fwith plenty of evening sunshine with
OL,7,Fclear skies following for many. Some
OL,8,Fpatchy cloud possible in the north
OL,9,Fovernight, but likely staying dry.
OL,10,FStaying clearer further south.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FSunny start for most,
OL,13,Fperhaps cloudier in the north, before
OL,14,Fthicker cloud spreads south through
OL,15,Fthe evening. Likely dry, but very
OL,16,Fisolated showers possible later. Very
OL,17,Fwarm again, but breezier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
