OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCooler
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells and showers Sunday,
OL,7,Fthese perhaps heavy at times. Dry
OL,8,FMonday, with lighter winds, variable
OL,9,Fcloud and sunny periods. Warm and
OL,10,Fsunny again Tuesday with light winds.
